{"title":"經導管心臟瓣膜治療技術","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"經導管心臟瓣膜治療技術","subtitle":"Transcatheter Valve Intervention — Mainz 2024 Fellowship Report","author":"謝慕揚醫師 Dr. Drake Mu-Yang Hsieh, MD, PhD","date":"2024-12-24","lang":"zh-TW"},"headingText":"關於本報告 About This Report","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\n本報告為新竹臺大分院心血管中心謝慕揚醫師於 2024 年 11-12 月赴德國美茵茲大學醫院 (Johannes Gutenberg University Mainz) 心臟瓣膜中心進修之成果報告。\n\nThis report documents the fellowship training of Dr. Drake Hsieh at the Heart Valve Center, University Medicine Mainz, Germany (November–December 2024).\n\n### 進修內容 Training Content\n\n- **M-TEER**: 二尖瓣經導管緣對緣修復 (Mitral Valve Transcatheter Edge-to-Edge Repair)\n- **T-TEER**: 三尖瓣經導管緣對緣修復 (Tricuspid Valve Transcatheter Edge-to-Edge Repair)\n- **TAVI/TAVR**: 經導管主動脈瓣膜植入/置換術 (Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation/Replacement)\n\n共參與 **125 例**經導管瓣膜手術：M-TEER 33 例、T-TEER 18 例、TAVI 74 例。\n\n### 語言版本 Language Versions\n\n- [中文版 Chinese Version](zh/index.qmd)\n- [English Version](en/index.qmd)\n\n---\n\n新竹臺大分院心血管中心 | National Taiwan University Hospital Hsinchu Branch, Cardiovascular Center\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n## 關於本報告 About This Report\n\n本報告為新竹臺大分院心血管中心謝慕揚醫師於 2024 年 11-12 月赴德國美茵茲大學醫院 (Johannes Gutenberg University Mainz) 心臟瓣膜中心進修之成果報告。\n\nThis report documents the fellowship training of Dr. Drake Hsieh at the Heart Valve Center, University Medicine Mainz, Germany (November–December 2024).\n\n### 進修內容 Training Content\n\n- **M-TEER**: 二尖瓣經導管緣對緣修復 (Mitral Valve Transcatheter Edge-to-Edge Repair)\n- **T-TEER**: 三尖瓣經導管緣對緣修復 (Tricuspid Valve Transcatheter Edge-to-Edge Repair)\n- **TAVI/TAVR**: 經導管主動脈瓣膜植入/置換術 (Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation/Replacement)\n\n共參與 **125 例**經導管瓣膜手術：M-TEER 33 例、T-TEER 18 例、TAVI 74 例。\n\n### 語言版本 Language Versions\n\n- [中文版 Chinese Version](zh/index.qmd)\n- [English Version](en/index.qmd)\n\n---\n\n新竹臺大分院心血管中心 | National Taiwan University Hospital Hsinchu Branch, Cardiovascular Center\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name"